-- Pimco’s Kashkari Likes Global Stocks Hon Hai, Honda, Samsung
-- B y   S r e e   V i d y a   B h a k t a v a t s a l a m
-- 2012-01-06T14:53:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-06/pimco-s-kashkari-likes-global-stocks-hon-hai-honda-samsung.html
Pacific Investment Management Co.’s
Neel Kashkari, who heads global equities at the  Newport Beach ,
California-based investment firm, said he likes international
companies including Hon Hai Precision Industry Co., Honda Motor
Co. and Samsung Electronics Co.  “We tend to like global market leaders with strong balance
sheets, and exposure to higher growth markets,” Kashkari said
today in an interview with Bloomberg Television’s Betty Liu.  To contact the reporter on this story:
